{
  "stem": "26022.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Now, the lift van was being auctioned off, or distributed to high-ranking Nazis or former underground [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] heroes, whatever-- to a select group of party members.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And that was done in an auction house on the outskirts of town.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And the auction houses were state-owned.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] And I-- we knew when that would happen.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Now came this big Edam.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And my mother and I both knew-- I mean, that's never going to cross our lips.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I mean, this is too valuable.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And when you need it, there is-- believe in God, don't believe in God, somehow, something happens.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So I took the Edam, and I went out to the outskirts of town to that auction house to the back entrance.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I had no plan.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Don't think that I'm so brilliant that I know what I'm doing.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "This was pure instinct.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I went to that auction house, to the back room, to the office.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there was a-- all of a sudden, I don't know English.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] What do you call that, sort of a half-wall between the public and the people who-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] what do you call that?",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I'm trying to-- I'm trying to think.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Does it have a special name, other than the way you describe it?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, like the-- the-- like, in a bar, you know that-- it's not a table.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's not a shelf.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's-- anyway, there were the-- the-- the people who made lists or did things.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there was the public.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And in between was a half-wall with a shelf on top, all right?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the public is here.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The others are there, like you have in some drugstores.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
